title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is being thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains highlight/map, an exception is being thrown.
SR: Steps to reproduce:  1. Open the attached report.  2. Locate a table that contains highlight/map.  3. Try to export the data from the table.  4. Observe the exception being thrown.
